public interface Icinga2

  • Method Details

    • processCheckResult

      @Produces("application/json") @Consumes("application/json") @POST @Path("/v1/actions/process-check-result") Map<String,​Object> processCheckResult​(@HeaderParam("Authorization") String authHeader, Icinga2CheckResult result)
      Update the status of a service or host.
      Parameters:
      authHeader - The authorization header value to authenticate with
